parameters.query:
INSERT INTO voice_messages (tenant_id, source_type, source_id, appeal_id, file_path, file_url, file_size, mime_type)
VALUES (
  '{{ $('Parse Upload').item.json.tenant_id }}'::uuid,
  'operator',
  '{{ $('Parse Upload').item.json.operator_id }}'::uuid,
  '{{ $('Parse Upload').item.json.appeal_id }}'::uuid,
  '{{ $('Parse Upload').item.json.file_path }}',
  'https://supabase.n8nsrv.ru/storage/v1/object/voice-messages/{{ $('Parse Upload').item.json.file_path }}',
  {{ $('Parse Upload').item.json.file_size }},
  '{{ $('Parse Upload').item.json.mime_type }}'
)
RETURNING id, file_url;
